ilm)|The Martian]]'' \u2013 [[Drew Goddard]]\n* ''[[The Revenant (2015 film)|The Revenant]]'' \u2013 [[Alejandro Gonz\u00e1lez I\u00f1\u00e1rritu|Alejandro G. I\u00f1\u00e1rritu]] and [[Mark L. Smith]]\n* ''[[Room (2015 film)|Room]]'' \u2013 [[Emma Donoghue]]\n|-\n! style=\"background:#EEDD82\" | [[Satellite Award for Best Animated or Mixed Media Feature|Best Animated or Mixed Media Film]]\n! style=\"background:#EEDD82\" | [[Satellite Award for Best Foreign Language Film|Best Foreign Language Film]]\n|-\n| valign=\"top\" |\n'''''[[Inside Out (2015 film)|Inside Out]]'''''\n* ''[[Anomalisa]]''\n* ''[[The Good Dinosaur]]''\n* ''[[The Peanuts Movie]]''\n* ''[[The Prophet (2014 film)|The Prophet]]''\n* ''[[Shaun the Sheep Movie]]''\n| valign=\"top\" |\n'''''[[Son of Saul]]'' ([[Hungary]])'''\n* ''[[The Assassin (2015 film)|The Assassin]]'' ([[Taiwan]])\n* ''[[The Brand New Testament]]'' ([[Belgium]])\n* ''[[Goodnight Mommy]]'' ([[Austria]])\n* ''[[The High Sun]]'' ([[Croatia]])\n* ''[[Labyrinth of Lies]]'' ([[Germany]])\n* ''[[Mustang (film)|Mustang]]'' ([[France]])\n* ''[[A Pigeon Sat on a Branch Reflecting on Existence]]'' ([[Sweden]])\n* ''[[The Second Mother (2015 film)|The Second Mother]]'' ([[Brazil]])\n* ''[[The Throne (film)|The Throne]]'' ([[South Korea]])\n|-\n! style=\"background:#EEDD82\" | [[Satellite Award for Best Documentary Film|Best Documentary Film]]\n! style=\"background:#EEDD82\" | [[Satellite Award for Best Cinematography|Best Cinematography]]\n|-\n| valign=\"top\" |\n'''''[[Amy (2015 film)|Amy]]'' (TIE)''' <br />\n'''''[[The Look of Silence]]'' (TIE)'''\n* ''Becoming Bulletproof''\n* ''[[Best of Enemies (2015 film)|Best of Enemies]]''\n* ''[[Cartel Land]]''\n* ''[[Going Clear (film)|Going Clear: Scientology and the Prison of Belief]]''\n* ''[[He Named Me Malala]]''\n* ''[[The Hunting Ground]]''\n* ''[[National Lampoon: Drunk Stoned Brilliant Dead]]''\n* ''[[Where to Invade Next]]''\n| valign=\"top\" |\n'''''[[Mad Max: Fury Road]]'' \u2013 [[John Seale]]'''\n* ''[[Bridge of Spies (film)|Bridge of Spies]]'' \u2013 [[Janusz Kami\u0144ski]]\n* ''[[The Martian (film)|The Martian]]'' \u2013 [[Dariusz Wolski]]\n* ''[[The Revenant (2015 film)|The Revenant]]'' \u2013 [[Emmanuel Lubezki]]\n* ''[[Sicario (2015 film)|Sicario]]'' \u2013 [[Roger Deakins]]\n* ''[[Spectre (2015 film)|Spectre]]'' \u2013 [[Hoyte van Hoytema]]\n|-\n! style=\"background:#EEDD82\" | [[Satellite Award for Best Original Score|Best Original Score]]\n! style=\"background:#EEDD82\" | [[Satellite Award for Best Original Song|Best Original Song]]\n|-\n| valign=\"top\" |\n'''''[[Carol (film)|Carol]]'' \u2013 [[Carter Burwell]]'''\n* ''[[The Danish Girl (film)|The Danish Girl]]'' \u2013 [[Alexandre Desplat]]\n* ''[[Inside Out (2015 film)|Inside Out]]'' \u2013 [[Michael Giacchino]]\n* ''[[The Martian (film)|The Martian]]'' \u2013 [[Harry Gregson-Williams]]\n* ''[[Spectre (2015 film)|Spectre]]'' \u2013 [[Thomas Newman]]\n* ''[[Spotlight (film)|Spotlight]]'' \u2013 [[Howard Shore]]\n| valign=\"top\" |\n'''\"[[Til It Happens to You]]\" ([[Lady Gaga]] and [[Diane Warren]]) \u2013 ''[[The Hunting Ground]]'''''\n* \"Cold One\" ([[Jenny Lewis]] and [[Johnathan Rice]]) \u2013 ''[[Ricki and the Flash]]''\n* \"[[Love Me like You Do]]\" ([[Max Martin]], [[Savan Kotecha]], [[Ilya Salmanzadeh]], [[Ali Payami]], and [[Tove Lo|Tove Nilsson]]) \u2013 ''[[Fifty Shades of Grey (film)|Fifty Shades of Grey]]''\n* \"[[One Kind of Love]]\" ([[Brian Wilson]]) \u2013 ''[[Love & Mercy (film)|Love & Mercy]]''\n* \"[[See You Again]]\" ([[DJ Frank E]], [[Charlie Puth]], [[Wiz Khalifa]], and Andrew Cedar) \u2013 ''[[Furious 7]]''\n* \"[[Writing's on the Wall (Sam Smith song)|Writing's on the Wall]]\" ([[Sam Smith (singer)|Sam Smith]] and [[Jimmy Napes]]) \u2013 ''[[Spectre (2015 film)|Spectre]]''\n|-\n! style=\"background:#EEDD82\" | [[Satellite Award for Best Visual Effects|Best Visual Effects]]\n! style=\"background:#EEDD82\" | [[Satellite Award for Best Art Direction and Production