edy|Best Musical or Comedy Series]]\n|-\n| valign=\"top\" |\n'''''[[Better Call Saul]]'' \u2013 [[AMC (TV channel)|AMC]]'''\n* ''[[American Crime (TV series)|American Crime]]'' \u2013 [[American Broadcasting Company|ABC]]\n* ''[[Bloodline (TV series)|Bloodline]]'' \u2013 [[Netflix]]\n* ''[[Deutschland 83]]'' \u2013 [[Sundance TV]]\n* ''[[Fargo (TV series)|Fargo]]'' \u2013 [[FX (TV channel)|FX]]\n* ''[[Mr. Robot]]'' \u2013 [[USA Network]]\n* ''[[Narcos]]'' \u2013 Netflix\n* ''[[Ray Donovan]]'' \u2013 [[Showtime (TV network)|Showtime]]\n| valign=\"top\" |\n'''''[[Silicon Valley (TV series)|Silicon Valley]]'' \u2013 [[HBO]]'''\n* ''[[Brooklyn Nine-Nine]]'' \u2013 [[Fox Broadcasting Company|Fox]]\n* ''[[Jane the Virgin]]'' \u2013 [[The CW]]\n* ''[[Sex & Drugs & Rock & Roll (TV series)|Sex & Drugs & Rock & Roll]]'' \u2013 FX\n* ''[[The Spoils Before Dying]]'' \u2013 [[IFC (U.S. TV channel)|IFC]]\n* ''[[Unbreakable Kimmy Schmidt]]'' \u2013 Netflix\n* ''[[Veep]]'' \u2013 HBO\n|-\n! style=\"background:#EEDD82\" | [[Satellite Award for Best Miniseries or Television Film|Best Miniseries]]\n! style=\"background:#EEDD82\" | [[Satellite Award for Best Miniseries or Television Film|Best Television Film]]\n|-\n| valign=\"top\" |\n'''''[[Flesh and Bone (miniseries)|Flesh and Bone]]'' \u2013 [[Starz]]'''\n* ''[[The Book of Negroes (miniseries)|The Book of Negroes]]'' \u2013 [[BET]]\n* ''[[Saints & Strangers]]'' \u2013 [[National Geographic (TV network)|Nat Geo]]\n* ''[[Show Me a Hero]]'' \u2013 HBO\n* ''[[Wolf Hall (miniseries)|Wolf Hall]]'' \u2013 [[BBC Two]] / [[PBS]]\n| valign=\"top\" |\n'''''[[Stockholm, Pennsylvania]]'' \u2013 [[Lifetime (TV network)|Lifetime]]'''\n* ''[[Bessie (film)|Bessie]]'' \u2013 HBO\n* ''[[Killing Jesus (2015 film)|Killing Jesus]]'' \u2013 Nat Geo\n* ''[[Nightingale (film)|Nightingale]]'' \u2013 HBO\n|-\n! style=\"background:#EEDD82\" | [[Satellite Award for Best Actor \u2013 Television Series Drama|Best Actor in a Drama Series]]\n! style=\"background:#E