ber                        = 20\n| award                         = Satellite Awards\n| date                          = {{Start date|2016|02|21}}\n| best_film                     = ''[[Spotlight (film)|Spotlight]]''\n| best_direction                = [[Tom McCarthy (director)|Tom McCarthy]] for ''[[Spotlight (film)|Spotlight]]''\n| best_drama_series             = ''[[Better Call Saul]]''\n| best_musical_or_comedy_series = ''[[Silicon Valley (TV series)|Silicon Valley]]''\n| last                          = 19th\n| next                          = 21st\n}}\n\nThe '''20th [[Satellite Awards]]''' is an award ceremony honoring the year's outstanding performers, films, television shows, home videos and interactive media, presented by the [[International Press Academy]].\n\nThe nominations were announced on December 1, 2015.<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/2015-satellite-award-nominees-announced-844739 |title=Satellite Awards Nominees Unveiled |last=Kilday |first=Gregg |date=December 1, 2015 |work=[[The Hollywood Reporter]] |accessdate=December 1, 2015}}</ref> The winners were announced on February 21, 2016.<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.pressacademy.com/award_cat/2015/ |title=Satellite Awards (2015) |publisher=[[International Press Academy]] |accessdate=February 22, 2016}}</ref>\n\nThe film ''[[The Martian (film)|The Martian]]'' led all nominees with nine, including [[Satellite Award for Best Film|Best Film]] and [[Satellite Award for Best Director|Best Director]] ([[Ridley Scott]]).\n\n==Special achievement awards==\n'''Auteur Award''' <small>(for singular vision and unique artistic control over the elements of production)</small> \u2013 '''[[Robert M. Young (director)|Robert M. Young]]'''\n\n'''Humanitarian Award''' <small>(for making a difference in the lives of those in the artistic community and beyond)</small> \u2013 '''[[Spike Lee]]'''\n\n'''Mary Pickford Award''' <small>(for outstanding contribution to the entertainment industry)</small> \u2013 '''[[Louise Fletcher]]'''\n\n'''Nikola Tesla Award''' <small>(for visionary achievement in filmmaking technology)</small> \u2013 '''HIVE Lighting Plasma Wizards'''\n\n'''Breakthrough Performance Award''' \u2013 '''[[Jacob Tremblay]]''' <small>(''[[Room (2015 film)|Room]]'')</small>\n\n'''Special Award for Breakthrough Comedian''' \u2013 '''[[Amy Schumer]]'''\n\n==Motion picture winners and nominees==\n[[File:Tom McCarthy (cropped).jpg|thumb|upright|[[Tom McCarthy (director)|Tom McCarthy]], Best Director winner & Best Original Screenplay co-winner]]\n[[File:Leonardo DiCaprio visited Goddard Saturday to discuss Earth science with Piers Sellers (26105091624) cropped.jpg|thumb|upright|[[Leonardo DiCaprio]], Best Actor in a Motion Picture winner]]\n[[File:Saoirse Ronan 2015 (cropped).jpg|thumb|upright|[[Saoirse Ronan]], Best Actress in a Motion Picture winner]]\n[[File:Christian Bale 2009.jpg|thumb|upright|[[Christian Bale]], Best Supporting Actor in a Motion Picture winner]]\n[[File:Alicia Vikander 2013.jpg|thumb|upright|[[Alicia Vikander]], Best Supporting Actress in a Motion Picture winner]]\n[[File:Aaron Sorkin at PaleyFest 2013.jpg|thumb|upright|[[Aaron Sorkin]], Best Adapted Screenplay winner]]\n[[File:TIFF 2018 Lady Gaga (1 of 1)-3 (cropped) (edited).jpg|thumb|upright|[[Lady Gaga]], Best Original Song co-winner]]\n\nWinners are listed first and highlighted in '''bold'''.\n\n{| class=wikitable style=\"width=\"100%\"\n|-\n! style=\"background:#EEDD82\" | [[Satellite Award for Best Film|Best Film]]\n! style=\"background:#EEDD82\" | [[Satellite Award for Best Director|Best Director]]\n|-\n| valign=\"top\" |\n'''''[[Spotlight (film)|Spotlight]]'''''\n* ''[[The Big Short (film)|The Big Short]]''\n* ''[[Black Mass (film)|Black Mass]]''\n* ''[[Bridge of Spies (film)|Bridge of Spies]]''\n* ''[[Brooklyn (film)|Brooklyn]]''\n* ''[[Carol (film)|Carol]]''\n* ''[[The Martian (film)|The Martian]]''\n* ''[[The Revenant (2015 film)|The Revenant]]''\n* ''[[Room (2015 film)|Room]]''\n* ''[[Sicario (2015 film)|Sicario]]''\n| valign=\"top\" |\n'''[[Tom McCarthy (director)|Tom McCarthy]] \u2013 ''[[Spotlight (film)|Spotlight]]'''\n* [[Lenny Abrahamson]] \u2013 ''[[Room (2015 film)|Room]]''\n* [[Tom Hooper]] \u2013 ''[[The Danish Girl (film)|The Danish Girl]]''\n* [[Alejandro Gonz\u00e1lez I\u00f1\u00e1rritu|Alejandro G. I\u00f1\u00e1rritu]] \u2013 ''[[The Revenant (2015 film)|The Revenant]]''\n* [[Ridley Scott]] \u2013 ''[[The Martian (film)|The Martian]]''\n* [[Steven Spielberg]] \u2013 ''[[Bridge of Spies (film)|Bridge of Spies]]''\n|-\n! style=\"background:#EEDD82\" | [[Satellite Award for Best Actor \u2013 Motion Picture|Best Actor]]\n! style=\"background:#EEDD82\" | [[Satellite Award for Best Actress \u2013 Motion Picture|Best Actress]]\n|-\n| valign=\"top\" |\n'''[[Leonardo DiCaprio]] \u2013 ''[[The Revenant (2015 film)|The Revenant]]'''''\n* [[Matt Damon]] \u2013 ''[[The Martian (film)|The Martian]]''\n* [[Johnny Depp]] \u2013 ''[[Black Mass (film)|Black Mass]]''\n* [[Michael Fassbender]] \u2013 ''[[Steve Jobs (film)|Steve Jobs]]''\n* [[Tom Hardy]] \u2013 ''[[Legend (2015 film)|Legend]]''\n* [[Eddie Redmayne]] \u2013 ''[[The Danish Girl (film)|The Danish Girl]]''\n* [[Will Smith]] \u2013 ''[[Concussion (2015 film)|Concussion]]''\n| valign=\"top\" |\n'''[[Saoirse Ronan]] \u2013 ''[[Brooklyn (film)|Brooklyn]]'''''\n* [[Cate Blanchett]] \u2013 ''[[Carol (film)|Carol]]''\n* [[Blythe Danner]] \u2013 ''[[I'll See You in My Dreams (2015 film)|I'll See You in My Dreams]]''\n* [[Brie Larson]] \u2013 ''[[Room (2015 film)|Room]]''\n* [[Carey Mulligan]] \u2013 ''[[Suffragette (film)|Suffragette]]''\n* [[Charlotte Rampling]] \u2013 ''[[45 Years]]''\n|-\n! style=\"background:#EEDD82\" | [[Satellite Award for Best Supporting Actor \u2013 Motion Picture|Best Supporting Actor]]\n! style=\"background:#EEDD82\" | [[Satellite Award for Best Supporting Actress \u2013 Motion Picture|Best Supporting Actress]]\n|-\n| valign=\"top\" |\n'''[[Christian Bale]] 