{"title_page": "Art Directors Guild Awards 2017", "text_new": "<div style=\"float: right; font-size: smaller; background-color:#ABCDEF; padding: 12px; margin-left: 5em; margin-bottom: 2em; width: 180px\" align=\"center\">\n\n'''22nd ADG Awards'''<br />\n<div>\nJanuary 27, 2018\n</div>\n----\nPeriod Film:<br />\n<big>'''''[[The Shape of Water (film)|The Shape of Water]]'''''</big>\n----\nFantasy Film:<br />\n<big>'''''[[Blade Runner 2049]]'''''</big>\n----\nContemporary Film:<br />\n<big>'''''[[Logan (film)|Logan]]'''''</big>\n</div>\n\nThe '''22nd Art Directors Guild Excellence in Production Design Awards''', took place on January 27, 2018 at the [[Hollywood & Highland Center]] Ray Dolby Ballroom in [[Hollywood]], honoring the best [[production designer]]s of 2017. Nominations were announced on January 4.<ref>{{cite web|last1=McNary|first1=Dave|title=\u2018Star Wars: The Last Jedi,\u2019 \u2018Dunkirk,\u2019 \u2018Lady Bird\u2019 Nab Art Directors Guild Nominations|url=https://variety.com/2018/film/awards/art-directors-guild-nominations-2018-star-wars-the-last-jedi-dunkirk-1202653098/|publisher=Variety|accessdate=4 January 2018}}</ref>\n\n==Winners and nominees==\n\n===Film===\n''' Period Film:'''\n* '''Paul Denham Austerberry &ndash; ''[[The Shape of Water (film)|The Shape of Water]]'''''\n** [[Sarah Greenwood]] &ndash; ''[[Darkest Hour (film)|Darkest Hour]]''\n** [[Nathan Crowley]] &ndash; ''[[Dunkirk (2017 film)|Dunkirk]]''\n** Jim Clay &ndash; ''[[Murder on the Orient Express (2017 film)|Murder on the Orient Express]]''\n** [[Rick Carter]] &ndash; ''[[The Post (film)|The Post]]''\n\n''' Fantasy Film:'''\n* '''[[Dennis Gassner]] &ndash; ''[[Blade Runner 2049]]'''''\n** [[Sarah Greenwood]] &ndash; ''[[Beauty and the Beast (2017 film)|Beauty and the Beast]]''\n** [[Rick Heinrichs]] &ndash; ''[[Star Wars: The Last Jedi]]''\n** [[James Chinlund]] &ndash; ''[[War for the Planet of the Apes]]''\n** [[Aline Bonetto]] &ndash; ''[[Wonder Woman (2017 film)|Wonder Woman]]''\n\n''' Contemporary Film:'''\n* '''[[Fran\u00e7ois Audouy]] &ndash; ''[[Logan (film)|Logan]]'''''\n** Stefania Cella &ndash; ''[[Downsizing (film)|Downsizing]]''\n** Rusty Smith &ndash; ''[[Get Out]]''\n** Chris Jones &ndash; ''[[Lady Bird (film)|Lady Bird]]''\n** Inbal Weinberg &ndash; ''[[Three Billboards Outside Ebbing, Missouri]]''\n\n''' Animated Film:'''\n* '''[[Harley Jessup]] &ndash; ''[[Coco (2017 film)|Coco]]'''''\n** William Cone and Jay Shuster &ndash; ''[[Cars 3]]''\n** Olivier Adam &ndash; ''[[Despicable Me 3]]''\n** [[Grant Freckelton]] &ndash; ''[[The Lego Batman Movie]]''\n** Matthew Button &ndash; ''[[Loving Vincent]]''\n\n===Television===\n\n''' One-Hour Period or Fantasy Single-Camera Television Series:'''\n* '''Deborah Riley &ndash; ''[[Game of Thrones]]'' (for \"[[Dragonstone (Game of Thrones)|Dragonstone]]\", \"[[The Queen's Justice]]\", \"[[Eastwatch]]\")'''\n** [[Bo Welch]] &ndash; ''[[A Series of Unfortunate Events (TV series)|A Series of Unfortunate Events]]'' (for \"The Bad Beginning: Part One\", \"The Reptile Room: Part One\", \"The Wide Window: Part One\")\n** [[Martin Childs]] &ndash; ''[[The Crown (TV series)|The Crown]]'' (for \"A Company of Men\", \"Beryl\", \"Dear Mrs. Kennedy\")\n** Steve Arnold &ndash; ''[[Mindhunter (TV series)|Mindhunter]]'' (for \"Episode 1\", \"Episode 4\", \"Episode 9\")\n** Chris Trujillo &ndash; ''[[Stranger Things (TV series)|Stranger Things]]'' (for \"Chapter Six: The Spy\", \"Chapter Eight: The Mind Flayer\", \"Chapter Nine: The Gate\")\n\n''' One-Hour Contemporary Single-Camera Television Series:'''\n* '''Julie Berghoff &ndash; ''[[The Handmaid's Tale (TV series)|The Handmaid's Tale]]'' (for \"Offred\", \"Birth Day\", \"Nolite Te Bastardes Carborundorum\")'''\n** Patti Podesta &ndash; ''[[American Gods (TV series)|American Gods]]'' (for \"The Bone Orchard\", \"The Secret of Spoons\", \"Head Full of Snow\")\n** Andrew Stearn &ndash; ''[[The Handmaid's Tale (TV series)|The Handmaid's Tale]]'' (for \"The Bridge\")\n** Anastasia White &ndash; ''[[Mr. Robot]]'' (for \"eps3.0_power-saver-mode.h\", \"eps3.1_undo.gz\", \"eps3.2_legacy.so\")\n** Ruth De Jong &ndash; ''[[Twin Peaks (2017 TV series)|Twin Peaks]]'' (for \"[[Part 1 (Twin Peaks)|Part 1]]\", \"[[Part 8 (Twin Peaks)|Part 8]]\", \"Part 15\")\n\n'''Half Hour Single-Camera Television Series:'''\n* '''Todd Fjelsted &ndash; ''[[GLOW (TV series)|GLOW]]'' (for \"Pilot\", \"The Wrath of Kuntar\", \"The Dusty Spur\")'''\n** Jessica Kender &ndash; ''[[Future Man (TV series)|Future Man]]'' (for \"Pandora\u2019s Mailbox\", \"Beyond the Truffledome\", \"A Date with Destiny\")\n** Amy Williams &ndash; ''[[Master of None]]'' (for \"Le Nozze\", \"Thanksgiving\", \"Amarsi Un Po\")\n** Richard Toyon &ndash; ''[[Silicon Valley (TV series)|Silicon Valley]]'' (for \"Hooli-con\", \"Server Error\")\n** Jim Gloster &ndash; ''[[Veep]]'' (for \"Omaha\")\n\n''' Multi-Camera Series:'''\n* '''Glenda Rovello &ndash; ''[[Will & Grace]]'' (for \"[[11 Years Later]]\", \"A Gay Olde Christmas\")'''\n** Stephan Olson &ndash; ''[[9JKL]]'' (for \"Pilot\", \"Lovers Getaway\", \"Set Visit\")\n** John Shaffner &ndash; ''[[The Big Bang Theory]]'' (for \"The Romance Recalibration\", \"The Separation Agitation\", \"The Explosion Implosion\")\n** John Shaffner &ndash; ''[[The Ranch (TV series)|The Ranch]]'' (for \"Last Dollar (Fly Away)\", \"Wrapped up in You\")\n** Stephan Olson &ndash; ''[[Superior Donuts]]'' (for \"Pilot\", \"Crime Time\", \"Arthur\u2019s Day Off\")\n\n'''Television Movie or Limited Series:'''\n* '''Joel Collins &ndash; ''[[Black Mirror]]'' (for \"[[USS Callister|USS ''Callister'']]\")'''\n** Jeff Mossa &ndash; ''[[American Horror Story: Cult]]'' (for \"[[Election Night (American Horror Story)|Election Night]]\", \"[[Winter of Our Discontent (American Horror Story)|Winter of Our Discontent]]\")\n** John Paino &ndash; ''[[Big Little Lies (TV series)|Big Little Lies]]'' (for \"Somebody's Dead\", \"Living the Dream\", \"You Get What You Need\")\n** Elisabeth Williams &ndash; ''[[Fargo (season 3)|Fargo]]'' (for \"[[The Narrow Escape Problem]]\", \"The Law of Inevitability\", \"Who Rules the Land of Denial?\")\n** [[Judy Becker]] &ndash; ''[[Feud (TV series)|Feud: Bette and Joan]]'' (for \"Pilot\", \"And the Winner Is\u2026\", \"You Mean All This Time We Could Have Been Friends?\")\n\n'''Variety or Competition Series/Awards or Event Special:'''\n* '''Schuyler Telleen &ndash; ''[[Portlandia (TV series)|Portlandia]]'' (for \"Portland Secedes\", \"Ants\", \"Fred\u2019s Cell Phone Company\")'''\n** Brian Stonestreet &ndash; ''[[74th Golden Globe Awards]]''\n** [[James Pearse Connelly]] &ndash; ''[[Bill Nye Saves the World]]'' (for \"Earth Is a Hot Mess\")\n** [[Keith Raywood]], Eugene Lee, [[Akira Yoshimura]] and N. Joseph DeTullio &ndash; ''[[Saturday Night Live]]'' (for \"Aziz Ansari/Big Sean\", \"Alec Baldwin/Ed Sheeran\", \"Larry David/Miley Cyrus\")\n** Bruce Rodgers &ndash; ''[[Super Bowl LI halftime show|Super Bowl Halftime Show Starring Lady Gaga]]''\n\n'''Short Format: Web Series, Music Video or Commercial:'''\n* '''Jason Edmonds &ndash; ''[[Star Wars Battlefront II (2017 video game)|Star Wars Battlefront II]]'': \"Rivalry / PS4\"'''\n** [[James Chinlund]] &ndash; [[Apple Inc.|Apple]]: \"Bulbs\"\n** Shane Valentino &ndash; [[Chanel]]: Gabrielle\"\n** Natalie Groce &ndash; [[Katy Perry]]: \"[[Bon App\u00e9tit (song)#Music video|Bon App\u00e9tit]]\"\n** Ruth De Jong &ndash; [[Nike, Inc.|Nike]]: \"Equality\"\n\n==References==\n{{reflist}}\n\n==External links==\n* [https://web.archive.org/web/20110714082001/http://www.adg.org/?content=cm&section=7 The winners and nominees on the official website]\n\n{{ADG Awards Chron}}\n\n[[Category:2017 film awards]]\n[[Category:2017 guild awards]]\n[[Category:Art Directors Guild Awards]]\n[[Category:2017 in American cinema]]\n", "text_old": "<div style=\"float: right; font-size: smaller; background-color:#ABCDEF; padding: 12px; margin-left: 5em; margin-bottom: 2em